				<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/d4fc0a824478e55c2a13386256efda66?s=44&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' />				<cite class="comment-author">					<a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.sylvainjutteau.blogspot.com">Sylvain JUTTEAU</a>
